seo: 漏洞生成,自定义漏洞等级,描述信息,请求ID
seo_en: vulnerability generation, customize severity, description, request ID
summary: 该插件用于根据请求ID生成漏洞信息，支持自定义漏洞等级、类型、描述、payload等详细信息，并提供修复建议。
summary_en: This plugin generates vulnerability information based on request IDs. It supports customizing severity, type, description, payload, and other details, along with providing remediation suggestions.
